SUMMARY:Part Closure: MILDMAY LINE: Saturday 24\, Sunday 25 and Bank 
 Holiday Monday 26 May\, no service between Camden Road and Stratford. Rail
  replacement buses will run as follows: Service S: Camden Road - Holloway 
 Road (for Piccadilly line) - Highbury & Islington - Canonbury - Dalston 
 Junction (for Dalston Kingsland) - Hackney Central - Homerton - Hackney 
 Wick - Stratford. Use alternative Overground services between Highbury & 
 Islington and Dalston Junction (for Dalston Kingsland). For Caledonian 
 Road & Barnsbury use local bus route 274 to/from Camden Road or walk to / 
 from Highbury & Islington.
